Overview:
A simple tool to batch convert .docx files to .pdf using an easy-to-use interface.


Requirements:
Windows OS
Microsoft Word (must be installed but no active subscription required)


How to Use:
Open the Program (MassConvertDocxToPdf.exe).
Input Folder: Select the folder containing your .docx files.
Output Folder: Choose the destination folder for the converted .pdf files.
Convert: Click "Convert" and let the program process the files.
Check the output folder for your .pdf files.


Troubleshooting:
Ensure Microsoft Word is installed on your computer.
Verify the folders you select exist and have write permissions.
Run the program as Administrator if needed.
